      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting an impeccable finish and a meticulously preserved interior that reflects a standard of care rarely encountered in the secondary market. Every component functions with precision, offering the discerning driver an experience indistinguishable from a new delivery. This is an investment-grade opportunity for those who demand excellence without compromise.",
