    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available now is an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering. This specimen features the S54B32 power plant, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing, providing a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip M-Variable differential. Critical preventative maintenance is complete: the rear subframe has been reinforced with structural plates, rod bearings have been replaced with high-grade treated shells, and the VANOS system has been fully overhauled with Beisan components. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, benefiting from refreshed bushings and an uncompromised factory suspension geometry. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior leather retains its original matte finish with no bolster wear. This is a turnkey, collector-quality example with zero deferred maintenance.",
